{"word":"H2220 - זְרֹועַ - zᵉrôwaʻ - zer-o'-ah - Arm","slug":"H2220","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">זְרֹועַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>zᵉrôwaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>zer-o'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Arm"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D6;&#x05E8;&#x05E2;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D6;&#x05E8;&#x05D5;&#x05E2;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D6;&#x05E8;&#x05E2;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D6;&#x05E8;&#x05D5;&#x05E2; - z<sup>e</sup>ro&#x0302;a&#x201B;  z<sup>e</sup>ro&#x0302;a&#x201B;  z<sup>e</sup>ro&#x0302;&#x201B;a&#x0302;h  z<sup>e</sup>ro&#x0302;&#x201B;a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>zer-o'-ah (1,2), zer-o-aw' (3,4)</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2232\">H2232</a>; the <i>arm</i> (as <i>stretched</i> out), or (of animals) the <i>foreleg</i>; figuratively <i>force: - </i>arm, + help, mighty, power, shoulder, strength."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H248\">H248</a>"}]}